net.sourceforge.fastupload

Class MultiPart

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.sourceforge.fastupload.MultiPart
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    MemoryMultiPart, MultiPartDiskFile

    public abstract class MultiPart
extends Object
    Abstract class represent content between two boundary, called a MultiPart, refer to RFC1867. A multipart contains content type, composition-data, name, and optional filename key value pairs, content bytes start behind them.
    Since:
    0.5.1
    Author:
    Link Qian
